window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>So you think your love can last forever...? Get married! </p> <p>Eighteen-year-old Ronit falls madly in love with Aisha the moment he meets her at his graduation day from a naval college. He believes he has found his perfect soul mate, and come what may, his love for her will last forever. Seven years later, he gets married to her. Big mistake! In a couple of weeks he completely hates her and believes she has turned into a devil. </p> <p>But his perception about love and life change when he hears the poignant love story of Shekhar, his Captain, on a ship that later gets hijacked by the pirates of Somalia. </p> <p>As they are left fighting for their lives, they confront if love truly can last forever.... But does it get too late?</p>"; 
